Comment: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:29.98,OP1,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you've got some time\Nto kill there all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the blonde brat\Nand that stuck up brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the middle of\Nthe tree climbing training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exceptional, so Kakashi Sensei told me to guard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a minute, Tazuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up, Giichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it a lot of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Building this bridge, \Nwill you let me quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so suddenly? Not you too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tazuna, I've had a bond\Nwith you from the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to cooperate,\Nbut if we push it too far,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gato will set his sights on us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if you get killed, everything is lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just stop building the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the bridge that everyone in town has built
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,believing that it would generate distribution and transportation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,for this poor Land of Waves that has few resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it goes so far as to take our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tazuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Giichi, you don't have to come anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:40.56,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,500)\c&HF8FAFC&}The country where the Hero existed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The country where the Hero existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to get some ingredients\Nfor dinner on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.70,Sign_4,,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(556,629)\c&H010106&\frz9.271}Will do any job
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whats with this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's hardly anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really surprised me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme some!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it's been ever since Gato showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, all the adults\Nhave turned into cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why now\Nthat bridge is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a symbol of bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.55,Sign_4,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000403&\blur1\frz19.79\move(556,503,513,504,0,3528)}I will \Ndo any job
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to restore their spirit \Nso they don't keep running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For the people of this land who have set their minds on remaining passive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can just complete that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This town will return to how it once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun... Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me that\NSasuke's still climbing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gradually catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let myself get distracted by Sasuke,\Nmy concentration will be disturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you give me some tips?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Without telling Sasuke, okay, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakra uses spiritual energy so you mustn't get tense or too eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and concentrate on the tree\Nso that you can constantly accumulate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a fixed amount of Chakra\Nin the bottom of your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate. Concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what the hell is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere while I'm trying to concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,U... Uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for him to speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You asked Sakura to give you some tips before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since we've had\Na meal with this many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop eating if you're going to vomit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to eat even if it means enduring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get strong as quickly as possible, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But vomiting is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, why is there\Na torn picture hanging here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari-kun was looking at this all through dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This torn part looks like someone who was\Nin the picture was deliberately torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man who was once\N called a hero of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always telling you not to\Ntalk about that person in front of Inari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying happened with Inari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears there's some kind of good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari had a father not related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like they were a real father\Nand son who got along really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then Inari was a child\Nwho laughed all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari has changed, ever since that incident with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The word bravery was eternally taken from the people of this island and from Inari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With that day,\Nthat incident, as the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That incident?\NWhat happened to Inari-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To explain the incident,\NI must first...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,tell you about the man who was called the hero of this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was around three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When Inari met the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Potchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Potchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Shooting Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, he's my dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not Shooting Star!\NHe's my Potchi! Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Potchi's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's going to give him\Nto the likes of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Potchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you wouldn't\Nhand him over quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I couldn't care less about that dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!\NAre you trying to kill Potchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! He's your special mutt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then save him, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay with you if he dies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm not okay with him dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my only friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, he can't even dog paddle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he's a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Potchi,\NI can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! If you're his owner,\Ndive in after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Akane-san.\NWhat if he can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go\Nsave him if you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't want to die, \Nsomebody save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Potchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Potchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna digress, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Potchi learned how to dog paddle then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Potchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting Star escaped, after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh... I can't breathe...\NThis... is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave those kids a good scolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this God? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you save me, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eat! Start with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You were betrayed by your dog too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In my country, dogs are creatures\Nthat have a keen sense of loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you betrayed\Nyour dog's trust first,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared and couldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I have no guts, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course a kid your age would be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a man choose a lifestyle you won't regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For things I truly hold dear to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect them until the very end with both these arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's tough, or sad,\NI'll stick it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it looks like I might lose my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was Kaiza and,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,he was a fisherman who'd come to this land\Nfrom another country in search of his dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Inari got attached to Kaiza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been because Inari\Nhad lost his real father
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,when he was too young\Nto remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was very attached to Kaiza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They were like father and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't take long\Nfor Kaiza to become
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a member of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was a man this town needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We... We've got trouble, Kaiza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The river dam has broken from this rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, District D will be flooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari, go get some rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we can do is\Nto attach a rope and pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense!\NHow are we going to attach a rope?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd die if we were to go\Ninto such a furious current!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we drag our feet,\NDistrict D will be annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you wouldn't be able to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad's unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad loves the town you're from, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For things I truly hold dear to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I lose my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect them to the end with both these arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!\NThe rope, the rope's attached!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on, the people of this land called Kaiza a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And he became a father\Nthat Inari could be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was around that time when Gato\Nset his sights on this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're going to protect this town with those arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This man resisted through force the policies of the Gato corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and disturbed the order of this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he will now be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope that such trivial matters\Nwill never occur again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Inari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That you'd... protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,me and the people of this land with both your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, Inari has changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as Tsunami and the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero, that's just stupid.\NThere's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had enough training for today.\NYou've used up too much Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die if you move any more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove that...
